1. *Slatka* mi je bila ova poseta. (This visit was sweet to me.)
2. Volim da kušam *slatke* stvari. (I like to taste sweet things.)
3. Ovo vam je *slatka* muka. (This is a sweet torment to you.)
4. *Slatko* je bilo gledati njihovo sreću. (It was sweet to watch their happiness.)
5. Sve što ona radi je *slatko*. (Everything she does is sweet.)